name: Tu Amore "Your Love" EP
description:
THIS PRODUCT IS CURRENTLY BEING RESTOCKED AND IS AVAILABLE IN EARLY 2014. GRAB IT DIGITALLY HERE
https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/your-love/id557595983

***************************************************

Tu Amore's DEBUT EP "Your Love"

Release Date 01/10/2012

Track Listing:

 1. I'm A Mess
 2. Bird in a Cage
 3. Speranza(featuring Mallory Knox)
 4. Wishing Well
 5. Joan of Arc (remastered)
 6. Love With No Limits (remastered)
 7. Charcoal

"They've created something that sounds fresh by managing to avoid cliches and use dynamics to great effect. Tracks like "Bird in a cage" and "Joan of Arc" are magnetic to the ears, and there is little doubt that the band have an eviable talent for arrangement" 7/10 - Rocksound

"Honest lyrics and dynamic melodies" 4/5 -  - Big Cheese Magazine

"Your Love’ is relaxing, perplexing and progressive at the same time and if you want to hear just how far rock music has developed in recent years, then it’s well worth wrapping your ears around." - Punktastic
